title: They’re not coming
description: They’re not coming. We’ve waited, we’ve gotten our hopes up…but they’re not coming. The inspirational elected officials, billionaires with promises of integrity, high-minded philanthropic organizations, all the institutions that were built to hold the high ground, to protect us and to even save us…are not coming.
